SubjectAppointment or Deployment of Alternates Exclusion Approval Order
PrecisOrder making the APPOINTMENT OR DEPLOYMENT OF ALTERNATES EXCLUSION APPROVAL ORDER in order to allow the operation of alternation provisions included in the National Joint Council Work Force Adjustment Directive and other similar work force agreements and instruments.
